# Git ignore rules for AMP Agency Agent System

# API keys — NEVER commit
resources/api-keys.md
**/api-keys.md
**/.env
**/.env.local

# Project folders — local work, not shared
projects/

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.obsidian/
*.swp
*.swo

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Node
node_modules/
npm-debug.log

# Local skill installs (install via npx, don't commit)
resources/skills/

# Logs
*.log
logs/
